metadata.name: The Beacon
metadata.description:
I was waiting for this day for four long years. The orange cat was created when the event was postponed for the second time and the black one was created when I said "ok, now it will finally come true". While testing on the test net I drew the girls with hope and positivity. 

Today is D-day. I MERGEd the drawings and created this historical memorabilia.
